igations because they interact directly with users. Design intent: keep a human coach as the final decision-maker for all training/nutrition outputs and never let AI output produce legal effects (GDPR Art. 22), so the system stays outside high-risk categories by construction (mandatory coach review/confirmation step before any AI-extracted plan is saved)."}, {"id": "webapp_templates_pages_legal_ai_transparency_concept_diet_import_ai_extraction", "label": "AI-based Diet/Workout Document Extraction (PDF/Excel)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "WebApp/templates/pages/legal/ai_transparency.html", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}], "edges": [{"source": "webapp_templates_pages_legal_ai_transparency_page", "target": "webapp_templates_pages_legal__base_template", "relation": "implements", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "WebApp/templates/pages/legal/ai_transparency.html", "source_location": "line 1 {% extends 'pages/legal/_base.html' %}", "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "webapp_templates_pages_legal_ai_transparency_page", "target": "webapp_templates_pages_legal_privacy_page", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "WebApp/templates/pages/legal/ai_transparency.html", "source_location": "line 144 {% url 'privacy' %} (sezione 5)", "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "webapp_templates_pages_legal_ai_transparency_page", "target": "webapp_templates_pages_legal_ai_transparency_concept_chiron", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "WebApp/templates/pages/legal/ai_transparency.html", "source_location": "lines 40-45 table row CHIRON", "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "webapp_templates_pages_legal_ai_transparency_page", "target": "webapp_templates_pages_legal_ai_transparency_concept_gpt_oss_120b", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_fil